                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5777" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0867</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8343 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被债务风暴席卷的“海航巨轮”</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The Debt Storm Swept HNA Group</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">金鑫，西尔扎提&#183;赛买提</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">浙江工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">海航集团有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">交通运输业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">多元化扩张；财务风险；债务危机；破产重整</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">diversified merger and acquisition; financial risk; debt crisis; bankruptcy reorganization</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">成立于1993年的海南航空股份有限公司，于1998年在海南航空的基础上成立了海航集团有限公司。2010年海航集团正式进入全球多元化扩张阶段，企业规模迅速扩张，企业经营业务从航空运输扩张到旅游服务、酒店、房地产、商贸金融等多个业务，总资产高达1.23万亿，跨入世界五百强企业行列。然而，由于海航集团进行盲目多元化扩张、高杠杆融资、资不抵债、新冠疫情冲击等原因，最终于2021年1月29日宣布破产重整。本案例通过对海航集团扩张之路的回顾，详细描述了海航集团因为扩张而逐步偏离航线陷入债务危机的过程，分析海航集团为摆脱困境而采取的自救措施以及疫情的冲击，引导学生分析海航集团进行破产重整的原因，帮助学生全面了解由企业盲目多元化并购引起的财务风险，深入思考多元化并购的财务风险管理。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Hainan Airlines Co., Ltd., was established in 1993, and HNA Group Co., Ltd. was established on the basis of Hainan Airlines in 1998. In 2010, HNA Group entered the stage of global diversified expansion. The scale of the enterprise expanded rapidly. Its business expanded from air transportation to tourism services, hotels, real estate, commerce, and finance, with total assets of 1.23 trillion, and was listed in the Fortune Top 500. However, HNA finally announced bankruptcy reorganization in January 29, 2021 due to blind diversification, highly financing leverage, insolvency, and COVID-19. By reviewing the expansion map of HNA Group, this case describes the process of HNA Group falling into debt crisis due to expansion, and analyzes the self-rescue measures and the impact of COVID-19. It guides the students to analyze the reasons for the bankruptcy reorganization of HNA Group, helps them fully understand the financial risks caused by the diversified merger and acquisition, and makes them to think about how to manage the financial risk caused by diversified merger and acquisition.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务报表分析》、《企业并购》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务风险</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021-12</td>
                            </tr>
